parameters: \.Miss? Now’s not the time to be a space case.
Who the hell are you guys?!
\.Can anyone seriously not explain what’s going on?!
\.Hm... By the looks of it, yes... How troubling.
\.\C[3]They seem too distracted to take any notice of me.
\C[3]In the center, there's a discussion happening
Before we get carried away, we should confirm what
But, I don’t even know where this is!!
We ran into quite a horrific experience earlier.
I’m afraid I can’t calm down at the moment...
\.\C[3]With a shiver, I touched my own neck.
\.\C[3]Everyone here had a collar put on them...!
\C[3]The discussion centered around the man in the
\.\C[4](Joe's there too, but he can't get a word in.)
\.\C[3]Finally, my head was starting to clear.
\.\C[4](...Why isn't Joe coming over to me?)
\.S-Sorry! Maybe that was too much force...
\.What are you saying? It’s me, Sara!
Did you seriously forget what your best friend
\.Hold up, could you be\fi the\fi Sara?! The\fi worst\fi swimmer
Don’t joke around like that! This is serious!!
Your pal Joe here wasn’t saying a word.
Wouldn’t even tell me his name.
\.I can assume that we’re all thinking the same thing.
\.All we know right now is who we are...
\.Hoho? And what do you have to say about our
Should ease the suspicion a little, at least?
\.I mean... not a whole lot else we can do.
\.What do you think, little Miss Sara?
\.Yeah... I’d be a lot more comfortable getting to know
\.See? The calm ones always know what to say.
It’s kinda creepy coming from a total stranger...
\.With that being said... once you’re ready, it’ll be
introduction time. Just tell me when, Sara.
Well then. Everyone ready for introductions?
\C[3]Looking right, I notice an especially restless woman.
\.Be quiet, meow!! You’re screaming in my ear, woof!!
\.H-Hey now...! F-Fighting’s not gonna get us anywhere!
\.\C[3]I could feel the tension in the air.
\C[3]I can feel the tension in the air.
\C[3]Some slightly calmer people are talking on the
Feels like we're wrapped up in somethin’ serious.
Yes... that seems to be the case.
\.\C[4](Huh... Have I seen this person somewhere?)
\C[3]There's two men keeping a watchful eye...
